---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="eCommerce Returns Management: Challenges and Best Practices - parcelLab"
  description="Explore the challenges retailers face with e-commerce returns management and best practices for improving the customer returns experience."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Returns</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">eCommerce Returns Management: Challenges and Best Practices</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Tobias Buxhoidt</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2023-03-22">March 22, 2023</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>8 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Returns and refunds are inevitable for e-commerce businesses, as customers can't see or touch the products before buying. Research indicates that 92% of respondents say a brand's returns policy sways their purchase decisions. Additionally, 62% of shoppers report they're unlikely to shop with retailers offering poor returns experiences.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Challenges in E-Commerce Returns Management</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F4373D" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">High Return Rates</strong> -- In 2022, clothing topped return categories at 26%, followed by bags and accessories and shoes at 19% each.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F4373D" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Reverse Logistics</strong> -- Managing return processes demands additional staff, expanded warehouse space, and dedicated departments.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F4373D" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Cost Considerations</strong> -- Returns in the US alone generate 15 million tons of carbon emissions and five billion lbs of landfill waste every year.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How to Improve the Returns Experience</h2>
        <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Include detailed fit information</strong> -- 33% of shoppers return items due to size and fit issues.</li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Highlight your return policy</strong> -- Display it prominently on every product page.</li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Optimize the returns process</strong> -- Create easy-to-use portals where customers generate labels or QR codes independently.</li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Use data and analytics</strong> -- Gather comprehensive returns data to reveal product and process issues.</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Product returns are inevitable in e-commerce. Communicating return policies and processes clearly builds trust and loyalty while implementing returns management solutions helps protect profitability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
